{"tid":1616721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無同情心 咪撚捐錢比義士","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T13:52:36.000Z","uid":287211,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22ac18de49450b695dd88665a0d6ffd439219da6","tid":1616721,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:49:57.000Z","msg":"講真 之前見到義士有困境要救濟的 Post 我一定問點交收之類 十居其十 都不了了之！因為我得不到回覆 所以做唔到。<br />\n<br />\n但同時在個post 總係有班人出來講 612基金點樣點樣<br />\n<br />\n我只是想講 唔好俾人利用自己的同情心 而藉此分化 就算唔分化都好 都會構成一定自我疑惑 動搖自己的想法<br />\n<br />\n總之 施與受 一切隨緣 我亦相信 要受的 一定找到施者 <br />\n<br />\n大家記得 對準政權 五大訴求 缺一不可 義士 香港以你為傲<br />\n<br />\n黑警死全家 我最撚鍾意吊狗個屎忽 因為夠緊"},{"pid":"b81d309d1bc09902fdff86be3a597ee523585813","tid":1616721,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:50:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f94e0c755674306ded3bc6bb37b90b2ad7028f2","tid":1616721,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"afe00bbb621cb4850027143ca57e5a833ba683a2","tid":1616721,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"黑警一條柒"},{"pid":"5ef866ea59ddbce734749be8af6b2f6b6cdecbff","tid":1616721,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:51:10.000Z","msg":"黑警叫雞唔俾錢"},{"pid":"b318b1fc408207271ebe9a43b44d67ed2c38477a","tid":1616721,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:51:37.000Z","msg":"認真推<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"30774a95bde0286050f40273d3493e8d45fb65e2","tid":1616721,"uid":157857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed2f9e71398985cd3faeae0176741ebd3e0e9166","tid":1616721,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:52:02.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"161ca1b63f48c4aec13f6b01bee3516665fb3713","tid":1616721,"uid":261180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0